					 根據網站的流量，你可能需要支付額外的費用。<br />
					 本外掛會將天氣資料快取 1 小時，以降低存取這些服務的頻率。<br /><br />
					 如果啟用天氣資料的功能，無論是否啟用 [地理資料]，皆<strong>需要</strong>填入 IPStack.com API 金鑰。','Enter your IPStack.com API key here. %1$sGet a free API key here%2$s.'=>'在此輸入你的 IPStack.com API 金鑰。%1$s從這裡免費取得 API 金鑰。%2$s.','Compatibility mode decides where to put the second, so called <code>&lt;noscript&gt;</code> or <code>&lt;iframe&gt;</code> part of the GTM container code.<br />
					This code is usually only executed if your visitor has disabled JavaScript for some reason.<br/>
					It is also mandatory in order to verify your site in Google Search Console using the GTM method.<br/>
					The main GTM container code will be placed into the <code>&lt;head&gt;</code> section of your webpages anyway (where it belongs to).<br/><br/>
					If you select "Manually coded", you need to edit your template files and add the following line just after the opening <code>&lt;body&gt;</code> tag:<br />
					<code>&lt;?php if ( function_exists( \'gtm4wp_the_gtm_tag\' ) ) { gtm4wp_the_gtm_tag(); } ?&gt;</code>'=>'相容模式的設定決定希望放置 GTM 容器的 <code>&lt;noscript&gt;</code> 或 <code>&lt;iframe&gt;</code> 部分的位置。<br />
