					<code>&lt;?php if ( function_exists( \'gtm4wp_the_gtm_tag\' ) ) { gtm4wp_the_gtm_tag(); } ?&gt;</code>','Container code compatibility mode'=>'GTM 容器代碼相容模式','Container code ON/OFF'=>'啟用/停用容器代碼','Manually coded (needs tweak in your template)'=>'手動輸入程式碼 (須要自己在佈景主題內調校)','Footer of the page (not recommended by Google, Search Console verification will not work)'=>'頁面頁尾 (Google 不建議這麼做，無法用來驗證 Search Console 的所有權)','Off (no tweak, right placement)'=>'停用相容模式 (無須調校，會安裝於正確位置)','Off'=>'停用','On'=>'啟用','Do not load GTM container on the frontend if role of the logged in user is any of this'=>'如果已登入的使用者擁有以下角色，將不會載入 GTM 容器','User roles to exclude'=>'排除以下使用者角色','Enter your custom domain name if you are using a server side GTM container for tracking. Do not include https:// prefix. Leave this blank to use www.googletagmanager.com'=>'如果你使用伺服器端 GTM 容器進行追蹤，請輸入你的自訂網域名稱。請不要包含 https:// 等前綴。如果此處留空，則會使用 www.googletagmanager.com 作為預設網域名稱。','Turn this on to prevent the plugin to flag orders as being already tracked.<br /><br />
