				只在你真的需要這項功能時啟用他。','Check this to fire dataLayer events after Contact Form 7 submissions (supported events: invalid input, spam detected, form submitted, form submitted and mail sent, form submitted and mail send failed).'=>'選取此選項，以在 Contact Form 7 送出表單後觸發資料層事件 (支援事件: 無效輸入、偵測到垃圾訊息、送出表單、送出表單且寄出電子郵件、送出表單但寄送電子郵件失敗)。','Cookiebot'=>'Cookiebot','Container domain name'=>'容器網域名稱','Cookiebot auto blocking'=>'自動阻擋 Cookiebot','Google Ads Business Vertical'=>'Google Ads 業務類型','To prevent duplicate transaction tracking at the order received page, enter the maximum age (in minutes) of the order or its payment for the transaction to be measured. Viewing the order received page of older orders will be ignored from transaction tracking, as it is considered to be a measured in an earlier session.'=>'請輸入計算單筆訂單的最大時效，以避免瀏覽訂單完成頁面導致重複追蹤交易。外掛會於追蹤交易時，忽略檢視舊訂單完成頁面的流量，將其視為已於前次工作階段完成的事件。','Only track orders younger than'=>'僅追蹤','Blacklist variables'=>'禁用變數','Blacklist triggers'=>'禁用觸發條件','Custom tag/variable templates'=>'自訂代碼/變數範本','Security'=>'安全性','Block all, except the checked items on all blacklist tabs (whitelist)'=>'除了下方選取的項目外，全部禁用 (啟用清單)','Allow all, except the checked items on all blacklist tabs (blacklist)'=>'除了下方選取的項目外，全部啟用 (禁用清單)','For example blacklisting everything and only whitelisting the Google Analytics tag without whitelisting the URL variable type will cause your Google Analytics tags to be blocked anyway since the attached triggers (Page View) can not fire!'=>'舉例來說，如果禁用除了 Google Analytics 代碼外的所有代碼，卻沒有允許啟用 URL 變數，將會導致 Google Analytics 遭禁用，因為相對應的觸發條件 (頁面瀏覽) 無法觸發。','Grouped Product Detail Page'=>'組合商品詳情','Enable this to add all order attribute into the data layer on the order received page regardless and independently from classic and enhanced ecommerce tracking (WooCommerce 3.x required)'=>'啟用本功能，不論使用的是標準或加強型電子商務追蹤，此功能會獨立建立一個資料層變數，在〈已收到訂單〉頁面中將所有訂單屬性納入資料層變數。 (須要 WooCommerce 3.x 以後的版本)','Order data in data layer'=>'訂單資料納入資料層變數','Weather & geo data'=>'天氣與地理資料','Enable this to 