					本外掛將會在所有頁面新增 %1$sAMP GTM 程式碼片段%2$s。','Google Tag Manager \'AMP\' Container ID'=>'Google 代碼管理工具 AMP 容器 ID','Do not flag orders as being tracked'=>'不要將訂單標記為已追蹤','Products per impression'=>'每次曝光商品數','Enable this to exclude tax from the revenue variable while generating the purchase data'=>'啟用本功能，在產生購買資料時，會將收益中的稅排除','Exclude tax from revenue'=>'未稅收益','Check this option to include a Tag Manager event when an existing user has been logged in on the frontend of your site (admin events not included)'=>'選取此選項，在使用者網站前端登入時，觸發代碼管理工具事件 (控制台內不會觸發)','User logged in'=>'使用者登入','Check this option to include a Tag Manager event when a new user registration has been completed on the frontend of your site (admin events not included)'=>'選取此選項，在新使用者於網站介面完成註冊時，觸發代碼管理工具事件 (控制台內不會觸發)','New user registration'=>'新帳號註冊','IPStack.com API key'=>'IPStack.com API 金鑰','Check this option to include the IP address of the visitor. You might use this to filter internal traffic inside your GTM container. Please be aware that per GDPR its not allowed to transmit this full IP address to Google Analytics or to any other measurement system without explicit consent from the visitor.'=>'選取此選項，將訪客的 IP 位址納入資料層變數。你可以用它搭配 GTM 容器篩選內部流量。請注意，根據《一般資料保護規範》(GDPR)，你不能在未獲得訪客明確同意的情況下，將完整的 IP 位址傳入 Google Analytics 或任何計測系統中。','Visitor IP'=>'訪客 IP','https://gtm4wp.com/'=>'https://gtm4wp.com/','(no geo data available)'=>'(沒有可使用的位置資料)','Incomplete Google Tag Manager environment configuration: either gtm_preview or gtm_auth parameter value is missing!'=>'不完整的 Google 代碼管理工具環境設定: 缺少 gtm_preview 或 gtm_auto 的參數值。','Misc'=>'雜項','Invalid gtm_preview environment parameter value. It should have the format \'env-NN\' where NN is an integer number.'=>'無效的 gtm_preview 環境參數值。正確格式為「env-NN」，其中 NN 為整數數字。','Invalid gtm_auth environment parameter value. It should only contain letters, numbers or the \'-\' and \'_\' characters.'=>'無效的 gtm_auth 環境參數值。正確格式應只包含字母、數字與連字號 (-) 與底線 (_)。','This does not seems to be a valid gtm_preview parameter! It should have the format &quot;env-NN&quot; where NN is an integer number. Please check and try again'=>'這似乎不是有效的 gtm_preview 參數值，正確格式應為「env-NN」，其中 NN 為整數。請檢查後再試一次。','This does not seems to be a valid gtm_auth parameter! It should only contain letters, number and the &quot;-&quot; character. Please check and try again'=>'這似乎不是有效的 gtm_auth 參數值！正確格式應只包含字母、數字與連字號 (-)。請檢查後再試一次。','Environment gtm_preview parameter'=>'環境參數 gtm_preview','Enter the gtm_auth parameter of the Google Tag Manager environment that has to be activated on this site. Both gtm_auth and gtm_preview parameters are required to activate the desired environment.'=>'輸入欲在本網站啟用的 Google 代碼管理工具環境參數 gtm_auth。必須同時輸入 gtm_auth 與 gtm_preview 兩種參數，才能啟用目標環境。','Environment gtm_auth parameter'=>'環境參數 gtm_auth','Check this to inclulde the full category path of each product in enhanced ecommerce tracking. WARNING! This can lead to performance issues on large sites with lots of traffic!'=>'選取此選項，以包含各商品的完整分類路徑，供加強型電子商務追蹤用。注意！如果是大流量的網站，很有可能導致網站效能問題。','Include full category path.'=>'包含完整分類路徑','Enable this to add all customer data (billing and shipping data, total number of orders and order value) into the data layer (WooCommerce 3.x required)'=>'啟用本功能以將所有顧客資料 (帳單、運送方式、總訂單數與訂單價值)納入資料層 (須要 WooCommerce 3.x 以後的版本)','Customer data in data layer'=>'顧客資料納入資料層','Add geo data (latitude, longitude, country, city, etc) of the current visitor (provided by ipstack.com)'=>'新增當前訪客的地理資訊 (緯度、經度、國家、城市等，資料來源為 ipstack.com)','Geo data'=>'地理資料','Check this option to include the username of the logged in user.'=>'選取此選項，將已登入使用者名稱納入資料層變數。','Logged in user name'=>'已登入使用者名稱','Check this option to include the post format.'=>'選取此選項，將文章格式納入資料層變數。','Post Format'=>'文章格式','Upsell Products'=>'追加銷售商品','Cross-Sell Products'=>'交叉銷售商品','Check this option to include the date of creation (registration) of the logged in user.'=>'選取此選項，將已登入使用者的註冊日期納入資料層變數。','Logged in user creation date'=>'已登入使用者帳號建立日期','Some product feed generator plugins prefix product IDs with a fixed text like \'woocommerce_gpf\'. You can enter this prefix here so that tags in your website include this prefix as well.'=>'部分自動產生商品動態資訊的外掛，會在商品 ID 前加上特定的前綴文字，如「woocommerce_gpf」。你可以在此輸入這個前綴，如此一來，你的代碼也能夠使用這個包含這個前綴的變數。','Product ID prefix'=>'商品 ID 前綴','Check this to use product SKU instead of the ID of the products for remarketing and ecommerce tracking. Will fallback to ID if no SKU is set.'=>'選取此選項，將商品貨號取代商品頁 ID，以供再行銷與電子商務追蹤使用。如果沒有商品貨號時，將回傳商品頁 ID。','Check this option to include the email address of the logged in user.'=>'選取此選項，將當前登入使用者的電子郵件地址納入資料層變數。','Logged in user email'=>'已登入使用者電子信箱','Check this option to include the ID of the author on the current post or author page.'=>'選取此選項，將當前文章或作者介紹頁面的作者 ID 納入資料層變數。','Site'=>'網站','Name of the current site in a WordPress Multisite environment'=>'在 WordPress 多站網路下，當前網站的名稱','Site name'=>'網站名稱','ID of the current site in a WordPress Multisite environment'=>'使用 WordPress 多站網路環境時，當前網站的 ID','Site ID'=>'網站 ID','Post author ID'=>'文章作者 ID','OpenWeatherMap API key'=>'OpenWeatherMap API 金鑰','Featured Products'=>'精選商品','Top Rated Products'=>'最高評分的商品','Best Selling Products'=>'最暢銷商品','Sale Products'=>'促銷商品','Recent Products'=>'最新商品',' (widget)'=>' (小工具)','Related Products'=>'相關商品','General Product List'=>'一般商品列表','Search Results'=>'搜尋結果','Enter your Google Tag Manager ID here. Use comma without space (,) to enter multiple IDs.'=>'在這裡輸入你的 Google 代碼管理工具的容器 ID。如果使用多個容器，請使用半型逗號 (,) 做區隔，並請不要在逗號後面加上空格。','Invalid Google Tag Manager ID. Valid ID format: GTM-XXXXX. Use comma without additional space (,) to enter more than one container ID.'=>'無效的 Google 代碼管理工具容器 ID。有效的容器 ID 格式為 GTM-XXXXX。在輸入多個容器 ID 時，請使用半型逗號 (,) 區隔，並請<strong>不要</strong>加上額外的空格。','This does not seems to be a valid Google Tag Manager ID! Valid format: GTM-XXXXX where X can be numbers and capital letters. Use comma without any space (,) to enter multpile container IDs.'=>'這似乎不是個有效的 Google 代碼管理工具容器 ID。有效的格式為 GTM-XXXXX，其中 X 可能是數字或大寫字母。如需輸入多個容器 ID，請使用半型逗號 (,) 做區隔，也不要在逗號後加上額外的空格。','Check this option to include the post id.'=>'選取此選項，將文章 ID 納入資料層變數。','Post ID'=>'文章 ID','Thomas Geiger'=>'Thomas Geiger','The first Google Tag Manager plugin for WordPress with business goals in mind'=>'第一款為商業用途考量製作的 WordPress 專用 Google 代碼管理工具外掛。','(no weather data available)'=>'(沒有可使用的天氣資料)','Settings'=>'設定','Notice: you should deactivate the plugin "Google Analytics for WordPress by MonsterInsights" if you are using Google Analytics tags inside Google Tag Manager!'=>'注意: 如果你已經將 Google 分析的追蹤碼埋入 Google 代碼管理工具，你應該要停用 Google Analytics for WordPress by MonsterInsights 外掛。','Notice: you should deactivate the plugin "WooCommerce Google Analytics Integration" if you are using Google Analytics tags inside Google Tag Manager!'=>'注意: 如果你已經將 Google Analytics (分析) 的追蹤碼埋入 Google 代碼管理工具，你應該要停用 WooCommerce Google Analytics Integration 外掛。','To start using Google Tag Manager for WordPress, please %1$senter your GTM ID%2$s'=>'在開始使用 Google Tag Manager for WordPress 之前，請先%1$s輸入 GTM 容器 ID%2$s','Media events'=>'媒體播放器事件','General events'=>'一般事件','WooCommerce'=>'WooCommerce','Browser/OS/Device'=>'瀏覽器、作業系統、裝置資料','Visitors'=>'訪客','Search'=>'搜尋','Posts'=>'網站內容','Google Tag Manager'=>'Google Tag Manager','Google Tag Manager for WordPress settings'=>'Google Tag Manager for WordPress 設定','Google Tag Manager for WordPress options'=>'Google Tag Manager for WordPress 選項','Author'=>'外掛開發者','Credits'=>'製作群','In some cases you need to rename the dataLayer variable. You can enter your name here. Leave black for default name: dataLayer'=>'有些狀況下，你需要重新替資料層變數命名。你可以在這輸入你自訂的名稱，或是留空保持預設名稱 dataLayer','dataLayer variable name'=>'資料層變數名稱','Advanced'=>'進階設定','Integration'=>'整合功能','Blacklist tags'=>'禁用代碼','Scroll tracking'=>'捲動追蹤','Events'=>'事件','Basic data'=>'基本資料','Google Tag Manager ID'=>'Google 代碼管理工具容器 ID','General'=>'一般設定','Invalid dataLayer variable name. Please start with a character from a-z or A-Z followed by characters from a-z, A-Z, 0-9 or \'_\' or \'-\'!'=>'無效的資料層變數名稱。請以英文字母 (a-z/A-Z) 為字首，後續字元僅限英文字母、數字、底線 (_) 或連字號 (-)。','Fahrenheit'=>'華氏 ℉','Celsius'=>'攝氏 ℃','Disable feature: control everything on Google Tag Manager interface'=>'停用: 透過 Google 代碼管理工具介面操控','This does not seems to be a valid JavaScript variable name! Please check and try again'=>'這似乎不是有效的 JavaScript 變數名稱，請檢查後重試。','Some info about the author of this plugin'=>'關於外掛開發者的資訊','You usually do not need to modify thoose settings. Please be carefull while hacking here.'=>'基本上你不需要調整這些設定。在使用這些進階設定時請三思。','Google Tag Manager for WordPress can integrate with several popular plugins. Please check the plugins you would like to integrate with:'=>'Google Tag Manager for WordPress 整合了許多熱門的外掛，請嘗試下列欲整合的外掛：','Do not modify if you do not know what to do, since it can cause issues with your tag deployment!'=>'如果你不知道該做什麼，請不要任意更改，因為這有可能會讓你在部署代碼時發生問題！','Here you can control which types of tags, triggers and variables can be executed on your site regardless of what tags are included in your container on the Google Tag Manager site. Use this to increase security!'=>'不論安裝什麼代碼於你的 Google 代碼管理工具容器中，你都可以在這裡控制是否在站內執行這些代碼或變數，藉此提高安全性。','Fire tags based on how the visitor scrolls through your page.'=>'根據使用者捲動頁面的情形觸發代碼。','Fire tags in Google Tag Manager on special events on your website'=>'在發生特定事件時，觸發 Google 代碼管理工具裡的代碼','* Browser, OS and Device data is provided using %1$sWhichBrowser%2$s library.'=>'* 瀏覽器、作業系統與裝置資料是由 %1$sWhichBrowser%2$s 提供的程式庫進行偵測。','Here you can check what data is needed to be included in the dataLayer to be able to access them in Google Tag Manager'=>'你可以在這裡勾選想要包含在資料層的資料，以供 Google 代碼管理工具使用','Use SKU instead of ID'=>'使用商品貨號 (SKU) 取代文章 ID','Contact Form 7'=>'Contact Form 7','Enable blacklist/whitelist'=>'開啟禁用清單/啟用清單','Enter the number of seconds after the the scroller user is being treated as a reader, someone who really reads the content, not just scrolls through it.'=>'輸入秒數，以判定捲動頁面的使用者是否為閱讀內容的讀者，而非隨意捲動頁面。','Scroller time'=>'捲動時間','Enter the DOM ID of the content element in your template. Leave it empty for default(content). Do not include the # sign.'=>'輸入佈景主題中主要內容區塊的 DOM 元素 ID。可以留空以使用預設值 (content)。不需要加入 # 符號。','Content ID'=>'內容 ID','The minimum amount of pixels that a visitor has to scroll before we treat the move as scrolling.'=>'判定使用者開始捲動多少像素後，才算真的在捲動頁面。','Minimum distance'=>'最小距離','Enter the number of milliseconds after the script checks the current location. It prevents too many events being fired while scrolling.'=>'確認當前位置後，再次確認位置的間隔時間 (毫秒)，避免在捲動過程中觸發過多事件。','Time delay before location check'=>'檢查位置前的時間延遲','Fire console.log() commands instead of dataLayer events.'=>'觸發 console.log() 指令，而非資料層事件。','Debug mode'=>'除錯模式','Enable scroll tracker script on your website.'=>'在網站中開啟捲動追蹤語法。','Enabled'=>'啟用捲動追蹤','Check this option to include a Tag Manager event when a visitor interacts with a Soundcloud media embeded on your site.'=>'選取此選項，以在訪客與嵌入於站內的 Soundcloud 媒體互動時，觸發代碼管理工具事件。','Soundcloud events'=>'Soundcloud 事件','Check this option to include a Tag Manager event when a visitor interacts with a Vimeo video embeded on your site.'=>'選取此選項，以在訪客與嵌入於站內的 Vimeo 影片互動時，觸發代碼管理工具事件。','Vimeo video events'=>'Vimeo 影片事件','Check this option to include a Tag Manager event when a visitor interacts with a YouTube video embeded on your site.'=>'選取此選項，以在訪客與嵌入於站內的 YouTube 影片互動時，觸發代碼管理工具事件。','YouTube video events'=>'YouTube 影片事件','Check this option to include a Tag Manager event when a visitor moves between elements of a form (comment, contact, etc).'=>'選取此選項，以在訪客於表單元素 (留言、聯絡表單等) 間移動時，觸發代碼管理工具事件。','Form fill events (gtm4wp.formElementEnter & gtm4wp.formElementLeave)'=>'表單填寫事件 (gtm4wp.formElementEnter 與 gtm4wp.formElementLeave)','Select which temperature units you would like to use.'=>'請選擇你希望使用的溫度單位。','Weather data units'=>'天氣資料單位','Weather data'=>'天氣資料','Check this option to include the type of device the user is currently using (desktop, tablet or mobile) including manufacturer and model data.'=>'選取此選項，將訪客目前使用的裝置類型 (桌機、平板或手機)，包含製造商與型號納入資料層變數。','Device data *'=>'裝置資料 *','Check this option to include the name and version of the operating system the visitor uses.'=>'選取此選項，將訪客目前使用的作業系統名稱與版本納入資料層變數。','OS data *'=>'作業系統資料 *','Check this option to include the name, version and engine data of the browser the visitor uses.'=>'選取此選項，將訪客目前使用的瀏覽器的名稱、版本與瀏覽器核心資訊納入資料層變數。','Browser data *'=>'瀏覽器資料 *','Check this option to include the ID of the logged in user.'=>'選取此選項，將目前登入的使用者 ID 納入資料層變數。','Logged in user ID'=>'已登入使用者 ID','Check this option to include the role of the logged in user.'=>'選取此選項，將已登入使用者的角色納入資料層變數。','Logged in user role'=>'已登入使用者角色','Check this option to include whether there is a logged in user on your website.'=>'選取此選項，以顯示目前訪客是否已登入。','Logged in status'=>'登入狀態','Check this option to include the search term, referring page URL and number of results on the search page.'=>'選取此選項，將搜尋詞彙、參照頁面網址與搜尋頁的結果數目納入資料層變數。','Search data'=>'站內搜尋資料','Check this option to include the count of the posts currently shown on the page and the total number of posts in the category/tag/any taxonomy.'=>'選取此選項，將目前頁面中顯示的文章數量，以及當前分類、標籤或任何分類法內含的文章總數納入資料層變數。','Post count'=>'文章數量','Check this option to include the title of the current post.'=>'選取此選項，將當前文章的標題納入資料層變數。','Post title'=>'文章標題','Check this option to include the date of the current post. This will include 4 dataLayer variables: full date, post year, post month, post date.'=>'選取此選項，將當前文章的日期資訊納入資料層變數。將產生四個資料層變數: full date、post year、post month 與 post date。','Post date'=>'文章/頁面發布日期','Check this option to include the name of the author on the current post or author page.'=>'選取此選項，將當前文章或作者介紹頁面的作者名稱納入資料層變數。','Post author name'=>'文章作者名稱','Check this option to include the tags of the current post.'=>'選取此選項，將當前文章使用的標籤納入資料層變數。','Tags of current post'=>'當前文章使用標籤','Check this option to include the category names of the current post or archive page'=>'選取此選項，將當前文章或彙整頁面的分類納入資料層變數。','Category list of current post/archive'=>'當前文章/彙整頁面所屬分類清單','Check this option to include the type of the current post or archive page (post, page or any custom post type).'=>'選取此選項，以納入當前文章或彙整頁面的文章類型 (文章、頁面或任何自訂文章類型)。','Posttype of current post/archive'=>'當前文章/彙整頁的文章類型']];